<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Challenge Feedback Notification</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        color: #333333;
        background-color: #f7f7f7;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .container {
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 20px;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #888888;
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <p>Hi {{StudentName}},</p>

      <p>
        Your teacher has shared feedback on your challenge 
        <strong>“{{ChallengeName}}”</strong>.
      </p>

      <p>
        Take a look at the suggestions and insights provided — this is a great 
        opportunity to improve your ideas and make your challenge even better! 💡
      </p>

      <p>
        If you have any questions or concerns, please reach out to your 
        <strong>School Admin</strong>.
      </p>

      <p>Best Regards,<br/>TruPreneurs.AI</p>
    </div>

    {{!-- <div class="footer">
      &copy; {{year}} Trusity. All rights reserved.
    </div> --}}
  </body>
</html>
